commodity Price and Return

Install and Load Packages to run the following code

install.packages("tidyverse")
install.packages("stargazer")
install.packages("lubridate")
library(tidyverse)
library(stargazer)
library(lubridate)

1.Soybeans Oil

URL="https://www.dropbox.com/s/fc4216loo2h1a2j/BO.txt?dl=1"
X<-read.csv(URL,header = FALSE,sep = ",")
names(X)[1]<-"Date"
names(X)[2]<-"Open"
names(X)[3]<-"High"
names(X)[4]<-"Low"
names(X)[5]<-"Close"
names(X)[6]<-"Volume"
X$MONTH<-as.numeric(substr(X$Date,1,2))
X$DAY<-as.numeric(substr(X$Date,4,5))
X$YEAR<-as.numeric(substr(X$Date,7,10))
X$D<-make_date(X$YEAR,X$MONTH,X$DAY)
BO<-X
BO_R<-diff(log(BO$Close))

1.1. Plot the Price

plot(BO$D,BO$Close,type = "lines",col="4",xlab = "Year",ylab = "Price")

1.2. Plot the Return

plot(BO$D[2:6343],BO_R,type = "lines",col="2",xlab = "Year",ylab = "Return")
